name: Keder The Black
Lore: 'A highly paid assassin and spy, Keder has infiltrated the Senate disguised as a Coruscant Guard. The identity of his target and his employer remains a mystery to all but him.',
Text: 'Deploys only to a site as an Undercover spy (-2 on Coruscant). During your control phase, may ''break cover'' to target one character with politics present. Draw destiny. If destiny +1 > target''s politics, target and Keder are lost.',
